===[[Etymology]]===
Greek ''kakos'' (bad) + ''kratia'' '''-cracy''' (to rule).

=== Noun ===

'''kakistocracy'''

#[[Government]] under the control of a nation's worst or least-qualified citizens. (More at http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kakistocracy; see also ''Kleptocracy'' at http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kleptocracy.)